                            <__p_name>load</__p_name>
                            <__p_description>Loads a project to this model from the given file path, closing any currently loaded project.</__p_description>
                            <__p_inlines>Read in the XML from the file with the given path.

Create a new qt XML stream reader from the loaded XML.

Read to the next start element and make sure it is the correct project tag.

Read to the next start element and read in the language name, making sure it is the correct language tag.

Read to the next start element and read in the project name, making sure it is the correct name tag.

Create a new project for this model using the read in language name and then set the project name to the read in name.

Read to the next start element and make sure it is the correct bock type tag.

Read in all block data from the root block XML element.

If any exception occurs then close the partially loaded project and raise it again.
</__p_inlines>
