                        <Function>
                            <__p_name>copy_to_xml</__p_name>
                            <__p_description>Copies the given indexes to XML.</__p_description>
                            <__p_return_description>A tuple of two items. The first item is copied blocks at the given indexes in the form of XML. The XML format is copy with each index an element in the root XML copy tag. The second item is a set of all block types that were copied.</__p_return_description>
                            <__p_inlines>Initialize the block types set and XML byte array.

Create a new qt XML writer stream attached to the byte array.

Write the start document and start copy element.

Write the language name text element.

Iterate through all given indexes.

Get the block of the index, writing its XML element and adding its type name to the set if it is valid.

Write the end copy element and end document.

Return the XML byte array and block types set.
</__p_inlines>
