                            <__p_description>Initializes a new spell highlighter with the given dictionary and parent.</__p_description>
                            <__p_inlines>Initialize the Hunspell object with the given dictionary, appending the root path and appropriate extensions.

Initialize the format style used for underlining misspelled words.
</__p_inlines>
