                <Class>
                    <__p_name>Text</__p_name>
                    <__p_description>This is the text dialog class. It inherits the qt dialog class. It is a plain text editor with optional spell checking and correction.

It is a plain text editor with optional spell checking and correction. Any misspelled words are highlighted and a button is provided that begins spell checking and correction. All spell checking features can be enabled or disabled at initialization of the dialog.
</__p_description>
